			"index": 1,
			"condition": "entryCondition=='firstTime'",
			"prompt": "<pitch mult='1.1'>This</pitch> is exciting, our <pitch mult='1.1'>first</pitch> radio listening. These are our <duration stretch='1.2'><pitch mult='1.3'>i</pitch></duration> heart radio stations. You can swipe back and forth to see them all, <pitch mult='1.1'>then</pitch> just <pitch mult='1.1'>tap</pitch> or <pitch mult='1.1'>say</pitch> the station you want.",
